There was a period of years there
where the life was so clear and clean.

1004
00:53:12,314 --> 00:53:14,024
Where did that life go?

1005
00:53:18,778 --> 00:53:20,572
How did it go away so fast?

1006
00:53:20,655 --> 00:53:23,575
Most of us think of Hulk Hogan
as the King of the Ring.

1007
00:53:23,658 --> 00:53:27,037
